content:
How do I add the [aalt](http://web.archive.org/web/20131016230006/http:/typophile.com/wiki/aalt) feature?

feature aalt {  
 feature locl;  
 feature onum;  
 feature case;  
 feature frac;  
 feature calt;  
} aalt;

Do I copy the lookups? For example, the local feature is local\_MOL and the lookup is sub Scedilla scedilla by Scommaaccent scommaaccent

Access All Alternates \< aalt \>  
 local\_MOL  
 onum\_latin  
 case\_latin  
 frac\_latin  
 calt\_latin

Thank you.
